the chairman of GM's German subsidiary, Adam Opel. He will meet them again
next week.
The dispute surrounds the move to VW of GM production chief Jose Ignacio
Lopez de Arriortua, taking several GM managers with him. Opel alleges the
former GM managers took industrial secrets with them.
