according to Insee, the state statistics institute, writes Alice Rawsthorn
in Paris.
News of the weaker figures took a toll on the Paris stock market where the
CAC 40 Index fell by 0.51 per cent to 2,128.20. The impact of the Insee
figures was aggravated by investors taking profits after the market's rise
