347 estate agents for less than a tenth of what it paid for them, a reader
received the following invitation from the estate agency arm of the
Woolwich: 'Don't let any old dinosaur try and sell your home. . . use the
most advanced selling techniques available. If it isn't Woolwich, it's
extinct]'
